      "text": "To the chief Musician, to Jeduthun, A Psalm of David. Truly my soul waiteth upon God: from him [cometh] my salvation.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 62:1",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA062.htm",
      "text": "For the Chief Musician; after the manner of Jeduthun. A Psalm of David. My soul waiteth in silence for God only: From him [cometh] my salvation.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 62:1",
      "source_id": "web",
